                'India is home to a rich diversity of GI-registered products — from Darjeeling Tea and Basmati Rice to Kanchipuram Silk and Mysore Sandalwood. GI registration protects these products from unauthorized use, ensures fair trade practices, and preserves the traditional knowledge and cultural heritage associated with them.',
